Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai da Burtaniya ya karu cikin sauri a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana da irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya, yana tabbatar da cewa duk da matakan da ke faruwa a ƙasashe daban-daban, cutar COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Idan aka yi la'akari da kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da wuraren da ake ba da gagarumin magani, ana bukatar a ƙara shirye-shiryen marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 da za su bukaci magani, musamman ma, gagarumin magani.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019, an samu wasu cututtukan cutar huhu a birnin Wuhan da ke lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
Ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa sabon nau'in coronavirus ne ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar, wanda yanzu ake kira cutar coronavirus ta nau'in 2 mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
Daga wannan lokacin, an kira cutar da SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
A cewar bayanai da ake samu a yau, kusan kashi 80 cikin dari na mutanen da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 suna kamuwa da cutar a cikin nau'i mai sauƙi, wato, kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin marasa lafiya suna warkewa.
Kimanin kashi 14 cikin 100 na COVID-19 sun zama na musamman kuma suna bukatar a kwantar da su asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin 100 na sauran suka zama na musamman idan ana bukatar ci gaba da magani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka kwantar da su daga COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin 100.
Wannan binciken ya bincika yanayin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da Burtaniya kuma ya kwatanta su da yanayin lardin Hubei na China.
Muna kuma kwatanta adadin cututtukan COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya da bayanan Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Bayan barkewar cutar COVID-19 a China, ta bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe, kuma a yanzu a sauran sassan duniya cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba daidai da yadda take a China.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, babban darektan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya sanar da annobar COVID-19.
A cikin mujallar Eurosurveillance ta 5 ga Maris, 2020, Mista Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da COVID-19 a Turai, wanda ya cika ƙa'idodin WHO don tantance cutar.
An fara samun mutum uku na farko a cikin EU/EEA a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020.  Dukkanin mutane uku sun dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano kamuwa da COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU / EEA 30 da Burtaniya, tare da a cikin lokaci daga 31 ga Disamba, 2019 zuwa wannan ranar, an sami kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 daga cikinsu, 17,750, gami da mutuwar 1,441, a Italiya kadai.
Gano yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da kuma kamuwa da cutar
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) a kowace rana a karfe 8:00 na safe tana sabunta bayanan adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka yi rajista a kowace ƙasa a duniya, daga kafofin hukuma kamar ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya na waɗannan ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da kuma WHO.
Ana amfani da wannan bayanan don nazarin yanayin yaduwar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta su da bayanan Italiya.
A matsayin ma'aunin yadda ake yada cututtukan COVID-19 na yau da kullun, an lissafa adadin cututtukan COVID-19 na kwanaki 14 tare da la'akari da yadda COVID-19 ke gudana a kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya a tsakanin Janairu 1 zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma nuna adadin adadin da aka samu a kowace ƙasa a karfe 8:00 na ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Hanyoyin ci gaban COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya
Yanayin ci gaban cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya sun yi daidai da yanayin da aka lura a lardin Hubei na China (Hotuna 1).
Yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya sun fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, kuma a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 an sami babban tashi a wannan ma'auni (ƙarin bayani).
Wannan ya kasance saboda yawan adadin cututtukan da aka samu a Italiya, amma a duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya, akwai irin wannan ci gaban COVID-19 (ƙarin bayani).
Hoton 2 ya nuna adadin adadin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da irin wannan a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Bisa ga wannan bayanan, adadin da aka riga aka samu a ranar 8 ga Maris, 15 a wasu ƙasashen EU / EEA da kuma Burtaniya, ya yi daidai da adadin da aka samu a Italiya kusan makonni 3 da suka gabata.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa an samu karuwar adadin mutane da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya.
Yanayin da ake gani na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ya ba da damar yin tunanin cewa annobar tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da bambancin matakan da ake samu a kasashe daban-daban, bambancin matakan da hukumomin kiwon lafiya na kasa ke dauka, da kuma yiwuwar bambancin ka'idojin gano cutar da kuma bambancin ka'idojin zabar marasa lafiya don gudanar da gwajin COVID-19, ciki har da gwaji mai yawa.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun ba da rahoton cewa kusan kashi 10 cikin dari na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 suna bukatar ci gaba da jinya, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun lura cewa asibitoci da wuraren jinya a waɗannan yankuna sun cika.
A halin yanzu, bayanai game da shigar da marasa lafiya da COVID-19 zuwa asibitoci da (ko) wuraren kula da matsanancin jinya a cikin EU / EEA suna samuwa ne kawai game da kashi 6 cikin ɗari da kashi 1 cikin ɗari na shari'o'in daidai (ba a gabatar da bayanai ba).
Amma, ana bukatar a yi tattara irin wannan bayanan a kai a kai don a cika bayanan da ake samu a yanzu, wato yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar da kuma yawan wadanda suka mutu.
A sakamakon binciken da aka yi a shekara ta 2010 zuwa 2011, an samu karuwar gado a wuraren da ake kula da marasa lafiya a Turai: daga 29,2 a Jamus zuwa 4,2 a Portugal a kowace mutane 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa wasu ƙasashe suna da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (wurin kwana 12.5 a cikin asibitoci masu tsanani da kuma asibitoci masu tsanani a kowace mutane 100,000 a 2010-2011).
Rahoton na shida na ECDC na sabunta sakamakon kimanta hadarin COVID-19 ya gabatar da yanayin samfurin kayan aikin tsarin kiwon lafiya tare da kimantaccen bayanan asibiti na COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, lokacin da haɗarin rashin gado mai sauƙi a cikin wuraren kulawa mai tsanani ya wuce 90%.
Tun da a halin yanzu ana rarraba cututtuka a cikin wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da na Burtaniya, kuma asibitoci da wuraren kula da gaggawa suna yawanci kula da yawan jama'ar wani yanki, ana ba da shawarar cewa a iya ba da bayanai game da cututtuka da yawan gado a wuraren kula da gaggawa a cikin na'urorin na biyu na Nomenclature na Ƙasar don dalilai na kididdiga (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya, annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri.
Saboda haka, dole ne kasashe, asibitoci da kuma cibiyoyin gaggawa su kasance a shirye don yanayin kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, wanda ba ya raguwa a cikin dogon lokaci, da kuma karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19, waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta likita da kuma gaggawa, wanda ake iya gani a yankunan da aka shafa na Italiya, misali.
Kamar yadda rahoton ECDC na baya-bayan nan na sakamakon kimantawa na haɗari ya nuna, hanzari, hanawa da kuma daidaitaccen tsarin aiki yana da mahimmanci don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2 daga ci gaba da ragewa zuwa rage tasirin, saboda, saboda ƙididdigar ƙaruwa mai sauri na cutar, masu yanke shawara da asibitoci na iya zama ba su da isasshen lokaci don yin tunani, ɗauka, da daidaita matakan da suka dace idan ba a yi hakan ba a gaba.
Rahoton sakamakon kimanta hadarin ya kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a da ake yi don rage tasirin cutar.
Kasashe suna da ɗan gajeren lokaci don ƙara ƙoƙari a cikin kula da su don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage nauyin da tsarin kiwon lafiyar su ke da shi.
Idan ba a yi haka ba, a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa, tsarin kiwon lafiya a wasu ƙasashen EU/EEA zai yi fama da yawan marasa lafiya da ke bukatar ci gaba da kula da su.
Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wanda cutar ta SARS ta 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ta haifar, ta zama bala'i ga bil'adama: a halin yanzu a China da sauran ƙasashen duniya fiye da mutane 3,000 sun mutu, kuma adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ya wuce 80,000.
Kamar cutar SARS-CoV ta homologous, wadda ta haifar da ciwon ciwon huhu mai tsanani a dubban mutane a shekara ta 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya kuma kamuwa da cutar daga linzamin kwamfuta kuma yana haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka ta amfani da irin wannan tsari.
