A cikin wannan labarin, mun gano kuma mun tattauna wani abu na musamman: Kwayoyin cutar da suka samo asali daga kwayar cutar ta mutum ba su da cutar a cikin tanki, amma suna da cutar bayan an watsa su zuwa sabon mai ɗaukar.
Muna kuma nazarin yanayin juyin halitta na kwayar cutar a cikin mutane, wanda ya nuna cewa yawanci ana samun karuwar cutar ta hanyar rage yawan kwayoyin cutar.
