Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sanar da annobar COVID-19
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanar da annobar cutar COVID-19, wanda cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta haifar.
