An sanya dukkan sansanonin sojin Koriya ta Kudu a cikin killace bayan an tabbatar da cewa sojoji uku sun kamu da cutar.
An yi amfani da shirin da ke tattare da binciken cutar don bincika mutane da cutar, saka idanu kan tuntuɓar su, da kuma tsara matakan killacewa ga waɗanda suka tuntube su. Wannan shirin an dauke shi mafi girma da kuma mafi kyau a cikin tsarinsa a duniya.
Hanyar yin gwaji ta ƙunshi sanar da duk waɗanda suka zo daga ƙasashen waje game da alamunsu ta hanyar wayar hannu, yin gwajin gwaji na cutar a rana mai zuwa, da kuma faɗaɗa damar gwaji don gwada mutane 20,000 a kowace rana.
An yi la'akari da shirin Koriya ta Kudu a nasarar yaki da cutar, duk da cewa ba a ware birane ba.
Yawancin 'yan Koriya sun sanya hannu kan takardun da suka yaba wa aikin shugaban kasar ko kuma suka bukaci a yi wa Mista Moon hukuncin kisa saboda rashin dacewar da suka ga gwamnatin ta yi game da barkewar cutar.
A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, an samu rahoton cewa Koriya ta Kudu ta sami mafi ƙarancin adadin kamuwa da cutar a cikin kwana ɗaya a cikin makonni huɗu.
A ranar 29 ga watan Maris ne aka samu sanarwar cewa daga ranar 1 ga watan Afrilu, za a sanya duk wadanda suka dawo daga kasashen waje a cikin killace na makonni biyu.
Rahotanni sun ce a ranar 1 ga Afrilu, ƙasashe 121 sun nemi taimakon Koriya ta Kudu wajen gwada cutar.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, Iran ta ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Kum, inda, a cewar Ma'aikatar Lafiya da Ilimin Lafiya, mutane biyu suka mutu a wannan rana.
Matakan farko da gwamnati ta ɗauka sun haɗa da soke kide-kide da sauran al'adu da wasanni, addu'o'in Juma'a, da rufe jami'o'i, manyan makarantu da makarantu.
Iran ta ba da riyal tiriliyan biyar don yaki da cutar.
A ranar 26 ga watan Fabrairun 2020, Shugaba Hassan Rouhani ya bayyana cewa gwamnati ba ta shirin sanya dukkanin yankunan da cutar ta shafa a cikin killacewa, amma za a sanya wasu mutane a cikin killacewa.
