A shekara ta 2008, Jami'ar Westminster a London ta gudanar da bincike wanda taron taron Turai na samar da takarda da kayan shafawa ya tallafawa; batun wannan binciken ya kasance kwatanta matakan tsabtace takarda, bushewar hannu tare da iska mai dumi da kuma kayan bushewar iska na yau da kullun don hannu.
An gano cewa bayan an wanke hannuwanmu kuma an bushe su a cikin na'urar busar da iska mai zafi, adadin ƙwayoyin cuta a yatsunsu ya ƙaru da kashi 194%, kuma a hannayensu ya ƙaru da kashi 254%.
Bayan an wanke hannuwanmu kuma an bushe su a cikin na'urar busar da ke da iska, adadin ƙwayoyin cuta a yatsunsu ya ƙaru da kashi 42 cikin ɗari, kuma a hannayensu ya ƙaru da kashi 15 cikin ɗari.
Bayan an wanke hannuwanmu da kuma bushe su da tawul, yawan kwayoyin a yatsunsu ya ragu zuwa kashi 76 cikin ɗari, kuma a hannayensu ya ragu zuwa kashi 77 cikin ɗari.
Mai bushewa mai iska mai iska wanda ke fitar da iska da saurin gudu 180 m/s (650 km/h, 400 mph), yana iya hura kwayoyin cuta daga hannayensu da kuma daga bangaren kansa kuma yana iya kamuwa da sauran masu amfani da gidan wanka da kuma sanus a cikin radius har zuwa mita 2.
Yin amfani da na'urar bushewa don hannaye mai iska mai dumi yana yada kwayoyin a cikin radius na mita 0.25 daga na'urar bushewa.
A shekara ta 2005, kamfanin TÜV Produkt und Umwelt ya gudanar da bincike don tantance hanyoyin bushewa na hannu.
