ACE2 (Angiotensin-transforming enzyme 2) wani enzyme ne wanda aka haɗa da farfajiya (ƙwayoyin halitta) na ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda da hanji.
ACE2 yana hana aikin enzymes masu canza angiotensin (ACE) ta rage ƙimar angiotensin-II da haɓaka Ang (1-7), yana mai da shi kyakkyawan bayani don magance cututtukan zuciya. AC2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin hanyar shiga sel don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta.
Ana kiran sigar mutum ta wannan enzyme hACE2.
Anjiotensin-mai canzawa 2  shine ƙarfe mai ƙunsar zinc wanda ke kan farfajiya na endothelial da sauran ƙwayoyin halitta.
Kwayar ACE2 tana dauke da nau'in N-farko na peptidase na M2 da kuma nau'in C-farko na jigilar renal amino acid.
ACE2 shine furotin membrane mai wucewa ɗaya na nau'in I, wanda ke da ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar cuta da sauran ƙwayoyin cuta.
Wani enzyme da ake kira sheddaze ya cire yankin ACE2 daga cikin kwayoyin halitta, kuma an fitar da furotin mai narkewa daga cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe an cire shi daga cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin yawancin gabobin: ACE2 yana haɗe da membrane na yawancin ƙwayoyin huhu na alveolar na nau'in II, ƙwayoyin gut na ciki, ƙwayoyin endothelial na jini da na jini da ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin jijiyoyin jijiyoyin mafi yawan gabobin.
Ana kuma lura da ACE2 da RNA a cikin ƙwaƙwalwar kwakwalwa, striautum, hypothalamus, da kuma ƙwaƙwalwar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine ya zama abin da ya dace da ACE.
ACE tana raba hormone angiotensin I zuwa angiotensin II.
ACE2, a cikin juyawa, yana raba amino acid na ƙarshe na carboxy na phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana hydrolyzing shi zuwa angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma yana iya raba wasu sauran peptides, ciki har da [des-Arg9] -bradykinin, orange, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita tashar tashar tashar SLC6A19 mai tsaka tsaki kuma yana kasancewa a cikin cutar Hartnep.
A matsayinta na furotin mai ƙwayar cuta, ACE2 yana aiki ne a matsayin babban hanyar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin halitta don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (ƙwayoyin cuta da ke haifar da SARS); da kuma SARS-CoV-2 (ƙwayoyin cuta da ke haifar da COVID-19).
A takaice dai, haɗuwa da furotin S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 zuwa yankin ACE2 mai ƙwayoyin halitta a saman sel yana haifar da endocytosis da kuma sauyawar duka ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma enzyme zuwa endosomes a cikin sel.
