A cikin SARS-CoV-2, irin wannan binciken ya yi niyya ne don lalata furotin mai kama da S, wanda ke taimaka wa kwayar cutar ta shiga cikin mai karɓar kwayar halitta ta ACE2.
Hanyar ta uku ita ce samar da alluran rigakafi bisa tushen nucleic acid (DNA ko RNA- alluran rigakafi, sabuwar hanyar yin allurar rigakafi).
Ana buƙatar gwada alluran gwaji da aka tsara ta kowane ɗayan waɗannan dabarun don aminci da inganci. A ranar 16 ga Maris, 2020, an fara gwajin asibiti na farko na allurar a kan masu sa kai huɗu a Seattle.
An bayyana cewa an yi amfani da maganin rigakafi don yin maganin SARS-COV-2 amma an yi jayayya game da wannan.
A watan Afrilu na shekarar 2020, an gudanar da gwajin asibiti sama da 300.
An gwada magunguna bakwai da aka amince da su don magance zazzabin cizon sauro, kuma hudu daga cikinsu sun yi amfani da su don maganin hydroxychloroquine ko chlorophyll.
Ana yin nazarin maganin rigakafin cutar a yawancin binciken da aka yi a kasar Sin; a ƙarshen Afrilu, an gudanar da bincike tara na III a cikin ƙasashe da yawa.
