A watan Maris na shekarar 2020, akwai bayanan farko game da yadda ake amfani da remdesivir.
An samu ci gaba a asibiti a cikin marasa lafiya da aka yi amfani da remdesivir a matsayin banda.
A cikin gwaji na III, an riga an gudanar da gwaji a Amurka, China, da Italiya. An yi nazari a China a watan Fabrairun 2020, kuma an samu sakamako na farko.
